  3.7613492521435204`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"98dbe493-2769-4395-a790-\
ae041cd6b67f"],

Cell["\<\
Both catchers run towards where the runner would be in one step. Also, the \
catchers want to be some distance away from each other to maximize the chance \
that they catch the runner.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7614203534958754`*^9, 3.7614203962196207`*^9}, {
  3.7615295036019325`*^9, 
  3.7615295338328285`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3ca8b244-6dea-4832-97f6-\
4da7805c8fca"],

