Cell["\<\
In the picture above, the catcher on the left is currently going towards the \
current position of the runner, not the position from a previous step.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7615340323327723`*^9, 
  3.761534095705462*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"19e45c54-9df1-4101-b207-\
