Cell["ii", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7614204969677*^9, 
  3.761420505307749*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a2353907-e26f-4dbf-bda0-\
e8523c591bb0"],

Cell["\<\
If the catchers employ the strategy from part i, the runner could go to the \
boundary and go in a circle. Depending on the initial position of the \
catchers, the runner will go a long time without being caught. Also, \
increasing the runner speed would make catching it nearly impossible.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7614206033382883`*^9, 3.761420621314229*^9}, {
   3.761420669272995*^9, 3.7614206903945227`*^9}, {3.761420751365498*^9, 
